snippet.title: DNF DUEL｜Battle Mage Main Trailer
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves for the arrival of the mesmerizing Battle Mage!  Embark on a journey where magic and spear techniques come together to create an unforgettable adventure. 🗡️🔮

Embrace the magic, feel the power, and prepare for an epic journey like no other! Battle Mage arrives on December 18th, 2023. ✨

#BattleMage #DNFDuel
